com.communote.server.web.fe.widgets

Interface WidgetConstants


  • public interface WidgetConstants
    This interface defines constants which are used by the widgets as parameters. Anyway most of ther parameter are depracted and should either be defined in the using widget itself or by using FilterWidgetParameterNameProvider
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
